<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>

<p>Rectangular <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType" reg="block">base or panel</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.46</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.33</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.25</measure>).</p></div><div type="description" n="text"><head>Description of Text</head><p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on a simple moulding (ll. 1, 2, 10) and within the recessed panel which it encloses (die, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.32</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.21</measure>) whose badly worn face may have been deliberately damaged.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.02</measure>; ligatured <foreign lang="grc">ΗΝ</foreign>, <foreign lang="grc">ΤΗ</foreign> in l.4, <foreign lang="grc">ΤΗΝ</foreign> l.6.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>Perhaps
<date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0300" exact="none">Second to third centuries A.D.</date>
(<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)</p>
</div>
